OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775149553
OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FResident doctors in England are to
OL,8,F"press ahead" with a planned walkout
OL,9,Fnext week after crunch talks failed to
OL,10,Favert the strike action, the
OL,11,Fgovernment has said, as it took a key
OL,12,Fpart of its offer off the table.
OL,14,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,15,FCare said an offer of 1,000 extra
OL,16,Ftraining places, which was part of the
OL,17,Fdeal on pay and jobs, will no longer
OL,18,Fbe "financially or operationally"
OL,19,Fpossible as the NHS prepares to deal
OL,20,Fwith the fallout from the strike.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]zD@DOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
