OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775149553
OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FTens of thousands of resident doctors
OL,8,Fin England are set to stage a six-day
OL,9,Fwalkout on Tuesday next week,
OL,10,Fimmediately after the Easter weekend.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday April 2, Prime Minister Sir
OL,13,FKeir Starmer gave the resident
OL,14,Fdoctors, formerly junior doctors,
OL,15,Fcommittee of the British Medical
OL,16,FAssociation (BMA) a 48-hour deadline
OL,17,Fto reconsider.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775149553
OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FAs the deadline approached, the BMA
OL,8,Fset out a list of demands for the
OL,9,Fgovernment which would need to be
OL,10,Faddressed for them to call off the
OL,11,Fstrike.
OL,13,FResponding, a Department of Health and
OL,14,FSocial Care (DHSC) spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"It is disappointing that the BMA has
OL,16,Fdecided to press ahead with strikes
OL,17,Fnext week, despite conversations we
OL,18,Fhave been having in recent days in a
OL,19,Fbid to protect the NHS from strikes."
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
