OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe DHSC maintained that the
OL,13,Fgovernment "offered resident doctors a
OL,14,Fgenerous deal to improve their pay,
OL,15,Fcareer progression and working lives
OL,16,Fthat would have seen resident doctors
OL,17,Fon average 35.2% better off than they
OL,18,Fwere four years ago".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
