FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775149553
OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"These posts would have gone live this
OL,8,Fmonth, but as systems now need to
OL,9,Fprepare for strikes and more
OL,10,Funcertainty, it simply won't be
OL,11,Foperationally or financially possible
OL,12,Fto launch these posts in April in time
OL,13,Fto recruit for this year ` this won't
OL,14,Fimpact the overall number of resident
OL,15,Fdoctors and the NHS will be there for
OL,16,Fpatients when they need it.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
