OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775149553
OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"Our attention and that of leaders
OL,8,Facross the NHS is now on protecting
OL,9,Fpatients, staff and our NHS by
OL,10,Fminimising disruption to the health
OL,11,Fservice."
OL,13,FThe deal offered to resident doctors
OL,14,Fincluded a 3.5% pay rise, the offer to
OL,15,Fcover some out-of-pocket expenses like
OL,16,Fexam fees and faster pay progression.
OL,18,FWhen Labour took office it offered
OL,19,Fresident doctors a 22.3% payrise.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
