PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775149553
OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FIn a statement issued on Wednesday
OL,8,Fevening, Dr Jack Fletcher, chairman of
OL,9,Fthe doctors' committee, said: "It is
OL,10,Fnot unexpected, but extremely
OL,11,Fdisappointing to see the government
OL,12,Fhas scrapped 1,000 new specialty
OL,13,Ftraining places at a time when doctors
OL,14,Fso urgently need more jobs and
OL,15,Fpatients so desperately need more
OL,16,Fdoctors.
OL,26,@qD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775149553
OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"It is genuinely disheartening to be
OL,8,Fat this point after what had been
OL,9,Fconstructive talks up until a few
OL,10,Fweeks ago when the government moved
OL,11,Fthe goalposts.
OL,13,F"It is simply wrong that the
OL,14,Fdevelopment of the doctors of the
OL,15,Ffuture is being used as a pawn like
OL,16,Fthis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
