OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775149553
OL,3,CGovernment withdraws extra training
OL,4,Cplaces after doctors fail to call off
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"We have consistently maintained that
OL,8,Fwe are willing to postpone industrial
OL,9,Faction should a genuinely credible
OL,10,Foffer be provided. This remains the
OL,11,Fcase now, up to, and throughout any
OL,12,Fperiod of industrial action."
OL,14,FNext week's walkout will be the 15th,
OL,15,Fand joint longest since the dispute
OL,16,Fbegan in March 2023.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
